{"title":"他们和瑞雪一同走来","authors":["荧光"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":2,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们和瑞雪一同走来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荧光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们和瑞雪一同走来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进菜市场去访问微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走下矿井去访问乌金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向雪被覆盖的越冬麦田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像迎接贵宾一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来马年丰收的年景。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们和瑞雪一同走来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是去高尔夫球场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更不是去灯红酒绿的舞厅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既无须警车开道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也无须前呼后拥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要简朴中的简朴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要热诚中的热诚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一只小小的银球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互撞着规格相同的球拍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那声声节奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恰和着亿万颗心的搏动！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三晋、南京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄浦江畔、南国花城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚下的座机还留有体温，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柜台前又响起笑声；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子夜慰问归来席不暇暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团拜会上又见身影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们累否？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——问人心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清晨，天安门广场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导人和士兵、工人、农民、学生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐仰视着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目送国旗上升……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗漫卷寒流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺着白雪与宁静。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}